==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chewink
<hw>Che"wink</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An
american bird (<spn>Pipilo erythrophthalmus</spn>) of the Finch family,
so called from its note; -- called also <altname>rufous-sided
towhee</altname>, <altname>towhee</altname>, <altname>towhee
bunting</altname> and <altname>ground robin</altname>.</def>
<altsp>[Also spelled <asp>cheewink</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cheyennes</ent>⟦br⟧
